text: Rishabh Sinha is an Indian actor. He is known for playing the role of Ayaan Ahmed Khan in Qubool Hai, participating in MTV Splitsvilla and Bigg Boss 9. He also played a negative role in the movie Kaanchi: The Unbreakable. == References == == Other websites == * * Category:1988 births Category:Indian actors Category:Living people
